headline: LaPour and Holualoa Announce Groundbreaking of Dual-Branded Marriott Hotel at City North, June 2025
summary: LaPour Partners ("LaPour") and Holualoa Companies ("Holualoa") are pleased to announce the groundbreaking of AC/Element City North, a new dual-branded hotel located in the CityNorth, a premier mixed-use development adjacent to Desert Ridge Marketplace in North Phoenix. LaPour and Holualoa purchased the site from Crown, the master developer.
